	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Make a modified emulator that gives lots of extra vblank time, and has a clean scanline interrupt system, then modify the game code to take advantage of this. Of course you'll have the original source code to the game, and you'll be using games that presumably don't do lots of tricky hardware stuff.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


