		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Make a modified emulator that gives lots of extra vblank time</div>
<br />
<br />Nesticle, the emulator we all love to bash for inaccuracy, already supports this. Just adjust the values in the "timing" menu and you should be able to eliminate slowdowns in Megaman and other poorly optimized games.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
